<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>NVIDIA on 潘文斌的技术文章</title><link>https://www.panwenbin.cn/tags/nvidia/</link><description>Recent content in NVIDIA on 潘文斌的技术文章</description><generator>Hugo</generator><language>zh-cn</language><copyright>2026 潘文斌</copyright><lastBuildDate>Tue, 16 Jun 2026 08:00:00 +0800</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://www.panwenbin.cn/tags/nvidia/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>Linux NVIDIA 驱动安装时的密钥签名</title><link>https://www.panwenbin.cn/posts/linux-nvidia-driver-sign/</link><pubDate>Tue, 16 Jun 2026 08:00:00 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://www.panwenbin.cn/posts/linux-nvidia-driver-sign/</guid><description>&lt;h2 id="起因">起因&lt;/h2>
&lt;blockquote>
&lt;p>在启用 Secure Boot 的 Linux 系统上安装 NVIDIA 显卡驱动时，需要对内核模块进行数字签名。每次更新驱动时都要处理密钥相关的选项，容易遗忘或配置不当，导致驱动加载失败。&lt;/p>&lt;/blockquote></description></item></channel></rss>